  Locus:
    Page: 368
    Verse: 12
Tags:
  - Power
---
If any man is rich and powerful he comes under the law of God by which the
higher branches must take the burning of the sun, and shade those that are
lower; by which the tall trees must protect the weak plants beneath them.
